1.0 (2014-07-21)
------------------

 * Initial DSLogic release by DreamSourceLab.


FoLogic 1.0 (2026-07-10)
-------------------------

 * Forked from DSLogic-fw-keil and rebranded to FoLogic
 * Adapted for FoLogic 16-channel 200MHz logic analyzer platform
 * Updated USB descriptor for FoLogic hardware (VID/PID)
 * Enhanced GPIF waveform definitions for FPGA interface
 * Added new command support for DDR3 buffer mode and stream mode
 * License upgraded to GPL v3
 * the fool - Porting, modifications and enhancements

